{
  "stem": "232.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only one I knew was one man in my age, one boy my age, who came together with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know only that, from the certain people, there's-- I am left, and the last one I knew was the-- the boy-- the boy who was with me, I lost contact in January 19-- in-- in Buna.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, as far as I know, I'm the only survivor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If this man lives, then we are two.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a French Olympian swimmer, French Moroccan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this time, it was like being French.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Nakache.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he was in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a young boy, maybe a year or so older than I, who was from Greece.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His name was Solomon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was boxing in-- in Buna for making-- getting a little bit more bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know him very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He is in Israel now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I know there came a movie out from him, but I never saw him back since I am from-- since I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to-- had to-- to pick up dead bodies form bombardments.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, that's not usually work, but it was very common in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When-- when somebody died, those people died on the-- on the march in, to make it harder for us to-- after 12 or 14 hours work at a camp-- at a-- at a work site, so to march in, we had to take two bricks and walk in, whole commandos with bricks, because the Germans wanted to build a new building.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't want to spend gasoline for the trucks, so they made inmates-- we were 10,000 of them-- imagine, if 10,000 people bring every day two or three bricks in, so they-- they-- they saved the-- the transportation.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
